reviewText:
In few words - this is the best fighting game on PC, no doubt.
+ Great netcode, you can play online without lags near every match;
+ Big character roster, each character has unique moveset and game tactics;
+ VERY cool soundtrack
+ Game is not so hungry 'bout system requirements;

- Medium-to hard threshold to the game, combo-attacks are not so easy to do;
- It's better to obtain arcade stick to play this game, 'cos it has a 6-button mechanics. Gamepad users can be frustrated about it (keyboard users is more happy);
- You can't choose character's alternative costumes, until you buyed them. Shame on you, Capcom
P.S. Beware of wake-up ultra's~
